data.description: Welcome to this charming split level home located in Tallmadge City Schools district. With 4 spacious bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, this home offers plenty of room. The owners have made thoughtful renovations, including removing a wall between the kitchen and dining room. This has created a generous amount of space, allowing for the addition of an island while still leaving room for a dining room table. Off of the kitchen the home also features a 3 seasons room, providing a peaceful retreat overlooking the backyard and patio. There are two living areas in this home, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The main level living area offers a comfortable space, while the lower level features a stunning stone fireplace that adds warmth and charm. Under the carpet in the living room and bedrooms, you'll find hardwood floors waiting to be uncovered and restored to their original beauty. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this house your home. Contact us today to schedule a showing and see all that it has to offer.
